resolution_criteria:
This question will resolve as the currency whose percentage increase relative to USD is largest among those listed in February 2026. If all currencies fall in value, then this question resolves as the currency that falls the least.
The percentage increase for each currency will be calculated as\frac{Close_{Feb 27} - Close_{Jan 30}}{Close_{Jan 30}}
where Close is its price in USD in the "Close" column on the corresponding Yahoo! Finance Historical Data page.
